data.description: Townhome with Convenient Access and Modern Amenities tucked away from the hustle and bustle, yet just minutes from the Interstate and a short drive to both Virginia Beach Oceanfront and Chic's Beach. It features three bedrooms, with two full bathrooms upstairs (one of which is ensuite to the primary bedroom, which also has a walk-in closet) and an additional half bath downstairs, making it easily accessible for families and guests. Recently updated with fresh paint throughout, the home boasts a welcoming atmosphere and cohesive look. The living area provides ample space for spending quality time with loved ones or hosting get-togethers, while the generously sized kitchen, complete with a breakfast area and bay window offers space and light for a myriad of uses. Plus, the property includes a low-maintenance backyard for unwinding around a fire pit on cool nights or enjoying summer afternoons under the shade. With low-maintenance living, you'll have more time to enjoy life!
